{
  "stem": "21004.9",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jaworow. ?] When I came to [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jaworow-- ?] and not to [INAUDIBLE], to Lemberg before that, a couple of days before, my wife ran away from [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jaworow. ?] She had a store, she was selling liquor, and baking bread, in delicatessen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this, this all come out, what's happened with my wife, how I find her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when the Russians, when you don't pay tax, if you make a lot of money, you have to pay tax.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They found once in her drawer, in the money they found a lot of rubles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she say, you have to pay $100,000 for the whole year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to pay $100,000.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She didn't have the $100,000 tax to pay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she ran away in middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She hired a truck and she went to Lemberg And in Lemberg she registered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All Polish Jews had the right, the Russians had to let them out to Poland, all Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was the pact, what they made with the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, when she came to Lemberg, she wrote me a letter, a letter that's and now come to Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or she is going to be there or not, I should stop in this and this place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was a Jewish officer, a big officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was in Lemberg and--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still remember his name-- [INAUDIBLE], him and his wife and a daughter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she left me a address.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'll come to Lemberg, because she'll have to give away to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am not back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So here and this and this address, I should come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he's going to direct me where she is going to be in Poland, because she's going to be corresponding to [INAUDIBLE], where I am.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
